Match the widgets with the events they might cause.

Widgets            Event Methods
check box      -   itemStateChanged(), actionPerformed()
text field     -   actionPerformed(), keyTyped(), focusGained()
scrolling list -   itemStateChanged(), mousePressed()
button         -   actionPerformed(), mousePressed()
dialog box     -   windowClosing(), focusGained()
radio button   -   itemStateChanged(), actionPerformed()
menu item      -   actionPerformed()